text: Eunidia lateraloides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1963. It is known from Borneo and Malaysia.BioLib.cz - Eunidia lateraloides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1963
